               Note that given other parameters of the model, the total levered firm valueTV(T,X*) is a function of onlyTandX*. The firm chooses these two variables to maximizeTV(T,X*). This is a simple unconstrained bivariate maximization problem, and a number of efficient library routines are well suited for this problem.12

